div(ng-include='"components/navbar/navbar.html"')
.container
  p
    | The delete server and server index api routes are restricted to users with the 'admin' role.
  table.table
    thead
      tr
        th Nick
        th IP
        th NPC
        th Hasher version
    tbody
      tr(ng-repeat='server in servers')
        td(ng-init='ip = ipToStr(server.ip)') {{server.nick || "-"}}
        td(ng-click="copyToClipboard(ip)")  {{ip}}
        td
          input(type="checkbox", ng-model="server.npc", ng-click="update(server)")
        td {{server.hasher == 0 ? '?' : server.hasher}}
        td.trash.glyphicon.glyphicon-trash(ng-click='delete(server)')